display_long_description:
Connect plugs and master logic gates in this educational game!

"Learn while you play: Familiarize yourself with the concepts of logic gates through fun interactive puzzles."
"Various levels of difficulty: Overcome different puzzles as you progress in the game."
"Variety of logic gates: Explore different types of logic gates, such as AND, OR, NOT, XOR, and more."
"Intuitive interface: Connect plugs by dragging cables and unlock exciting new stages."

Begin your adventure in tutorial mode, designed to teach you the different types of logic gates. You'll learn about AND, OR, NOT, XOR gates, and many more as you explore their functions and characteristics.

Once you've mastered logic gates, it's time to test your skills in gameplay mode. Get ready to tackle a series of random puzzles that will challenge your logic and dexterity. In each level, you'll be presented with a panel of plugs, and your goal is to strategically connect them to complete the circuit correctly.
